display_name: For women: Intro to Coding Workshop
text:
\*FOR WOMEN ONLY\*

Are you a female immigrant or refugee who has no idea about coding and is curious to know more about it? This presentation is for you!

Join us at Futurekids in Lausanne on Monday January 27th from 1.30pm to 4.00pm! Olga, an IT woman, will do a short presentation about coding and will answer your questions.

The event is FREE - sign up now!
